Package: plastic
Title: plastic
Version: 1.0
Description: PLASTIC (Predictive Landscape Analysis of Single-cell Transcriptomes for Identifying Cancer) is an algorithm for estimating epigenetic reprogramming and cellular plasticity from single-cell or single-nucleus RNA-Seq data. It builds upon our previous CancerStemID, SCENT and SCIRA algorithm, adding functionality.
Date: 2025-8-10
Author: Andrew E Teschendorff
Maintainer: Andrew Teschendorff <andrew@sinh.ac.cn>
Depends: R (>= 4.4.2)
